<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我听错了吧</font>

4
00:00:16,529 --> 00:00:21,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这可不是在飞行高度1万米的客机中会说的话</font>

5
00:00:21,739 --> 00:00:24,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以肯定是我听错了 误会了</font>

6
00:00:24,659 --> 00:00:26,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">希望是如此吧</font>

7
00:00:27,069 --> 00:00:30,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">从以前开始 我就经常会遭遇麻烦</font>

8
00:00:31,249 --> 00:00:33,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也许该说是招灾体质吧</font>

9
00:00:34,469 --> 00:00:37,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">走在大道上会被拉去参加快闪</font>

10
00:00:37,829 --> 00:00:41,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">走在小巷里会目击毒品交易现场</font>

11
00:00:41,359 --> 00:00:43,329
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为经常出现在杀人现场</font>

12
00:00:43,429 --> 00:00:45,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">经常看到我的警察总是会怀疑我</font>

13
00:00:46,639 --> 00:00:48,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而今天也是…</font>

14
00:00:50,369 --> 00:00:55,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我被人塞了个不知道里面有什么东西的大提箱</font>

15
00:00:55,029 --> 00:00:56,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">然后要我坐飞机出国</font>

16
00:00:58,369 --> 00:01:00,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">莫名其妙 不讲道理</font>

17
00:01:01,159 --> 00:01:06,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而且 一般来说 这种情况下需要的人是医生和护士吧</font>

18
00:01:07,099 --> 00:01:08,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">结果却找侦探？</font>

19
00:01:09,869 --> 00:01:12,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">请问乘客之中有没有侦探？</font>

20
00:01:14,079 --> 00:01:16,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">看来不是我听错了</font>

21
00:01:16,949 --> 00:01:21,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 就算这样也无妨 毕竟我又不是侦探</font>

22
00:01:21,329 --> 00:01:21,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我</font>

23
00:01:22,719 --> 00:01:24,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我是侦探</font>

24
00:01:32,409 --> 00:01:34,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 你叫什么名字？</font>

25
00:01:40,439 --> 00:01:42,549
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我怎么这么冒昧</font>

26
00:01:46,609 --> 00:01:48,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你来得正好</font>

27
00:01:50,449 --> 00:01:52,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">来当我的助手吧</font>

28
00:01:55,369 --> 00:01:55,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">啥？</font>

29
00:01:58,469 --> 00:02:00,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我是侦探 这位是助手</font>

30
00:02:03,019 --> 00:02:03,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">请跟我来</font>

31
00:02:05,089 --> 00:02:07,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 这到底是…</font>

32
00:02:11,619 --> 00:02:12,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔</font>

33
00:02:13,159 --> 00:02:14,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔？</font>

34
00:02:14,949 --> 00:02:16,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是我的名字</font>

35
00:02:17,309 --> 00:02:18,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这名字真奇怪
(“谢丝塔”音同西班牙语的“siesta”，意为“午睡”。)</font>

36
00:02:19,079 --> 00:02:20,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是代号</font>

37
00:02:20,449 --> 00:02:21,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">代号？</font>

38
00:02:21,699 --> 00:02:22,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一般人都会有的</font>

39
00:02:23,059 --> 00:02:24,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一般人不会有的</font>

40
00:02:26,099 --> 00:02:27,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你叫什么名字？</font>

41
00:02:27,929 --> 00:02:29,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">君冢君彦</font>

42
00:02:29,729 --> 00:02:32,309
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗 那以后我就叫「君」了</font>

43
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:36,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是昵称？又或者只是第二人称？
(“君”这个汉字念成kimi的时候，在日语中有“你”的意思。)</font>

44
00:02:38,439 --> 00:02:39,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你觉得呢？</font>

45
00:02:44,819 --> 00:02:47,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我把侦探和助手带来了</font>

46
00:02:54,169 --> 00:02:56,649
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真的有侦探啊</font>

47
00:02:58,089 --> 00:03:00,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">比我想象的还要年轻</font>

48
00:03:01,909 --> 00:03:03,619
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哪位是侦探？</font>

49
00:03:04,519 --> 00:03:07,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是能想象到的最糟糕的情况</font>

50
00:03:07,899 --> 00:03:10,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">比起问问题 该先报上你的大名吧？</font>

51
00:03:13,509 --> 00:03:16,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">蝙蝠 不过只是代号</font>

52
00:03:16,979 --> 00:03:17,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">看</font>

53
00:03:19,229 --> 00:03:21,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大家都有代号啊</font>

54
00:03:21,779 --> 00:03:23,159
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我管你啊！</font>

55
00:03:23,159 --> 00:03:26,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">根本没什么好在意的 现在也不是说这个的时候！</font>

56
00:03:26,869 --> 00:03:29,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我是谢丝塔 这位是助手华生</font>

57
00:03:30,339 --> 00:03:32,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我们是在贝克街一起出生长大的</font>

58
00:03:33,999 --> 00:03:34,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那么</font>

59
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:37,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">蝙蝠 你有什么目的？</font>

60
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:41,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么要把我这个大侦探叫到这里来？</font>

61
00:03:43,339 --> 00:03:44,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这女人真有意思</font>

62
00:03:45,489 --> 00:03:50,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好吧 既然如此 你就来推理一下我劫持这架飞机的原因</font>

63
00:03:50,709 --> 00:03:54,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如果能答对 我就不拧断机长的脖子了</font>

64
00:03:57,969 --> 00:04:01,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你叫我们来 就只是为了推理这个？</font>

65
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:04,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对 正是如此 这是一场游戏</font>

66
00:04:05,129 --> 00:04:08,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">关系到机组和乘客共600条生命的死亡游戏</font>

67
00:04:08,839 --> 00:04:10,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">很令人兴奋吧？</font>

68
00:04:11,039 --> 00:04:17,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你们的通关条件 就只是猜中我劫机的原因</font>

69
00:04:17,639 --> 00:04:22,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">成功就所有人都能活命 失败就都死？</font>

70
00:04:22,899 --> 00:04:25,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对 很简单的规则吧</font>

71
00:04:25,969 --> 00:04:32,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是的 但如果我们失败了 你也和我们一样会死</font>

72
00:04:32,629 --> 00:04:34,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你就不在乎自己的性命吗？</font>

73
00:04:35,159 --> 00:04:39,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大概是因为不这样我就体会不到生命的真实感吧</font>

74
00:04:40,729 --> 00:04:43,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗 你可真是个闲人</font>

75
00:04:43,799 --> 00:04:49,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是啊 我很闲 闲到不小心劫了个机</font>

76
00:04:49,669 --> 00:04:52,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好 那这就是答案了</font>

77
00:04:53,869 --> 00:04:57,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你就是闲得发慌了才来劫机</font>

78
00:05:00,199 --> 00:05:01,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是最后答案</font>

79
00:05:05,199 --> 00:05:08,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你等等 你这是认真的吗？</font>

80
00:05:08,629 --> 00:05:11,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这答案可关系到所有乘客的命啊</font>

81
00:05:12,159 --> 00:05:13,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为…</font>

82
00:05:14,159 --> 00:05:15,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这男人自己都说了啊</font>

83
00:05:16,189 --> 00:05:20,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">「我很闲 闲到不小心劫了个机」</font>

84
00:05:21,289 --> 00:05:25,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">他确实是这么说的 但这不就只是随便说笑而已吗</font>

85
00:05:25,579 --> 00:05:29,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦 那你的意思是 这个男人在骗人？</font>

86
00:05:31,039 --> 00:05:32,749
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为畏惧我这个大侦探</font>

87
00:05:33,089 --> 00:05:36,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">把不小心说漏嘴的事情当成说笑想要蒙混过去</font>

88
00:05:36,799 --> 00:05:40,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">强行说我输了 以此来结束游戏</font>

89
00:05:41,309 --> 00:05:42,159
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也就是说…</font>

90
00:05:42,799 --> 00:05:44,139
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">他怕了</font>

91
00:05:46,629 --> 00:05:47,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是这样的吗？</font>

92
00:05:57,039 --> 00:05:59,319
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">行啊 你真行啊</font>

93
00:05:59,739 --> 00:06:02,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哎呀 厉害 太厉害了</font>

94
00:06:02,589 --> 00:06:06,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没想到会被人用这种方式给钓了</font>

95
00:06:08,279 --> 00:06:12,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然这结果比想象中要无聊 但也算了</font>

96
00:06:12,669 --> 00:06:17,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">反正目的已经实现 那就直接收手吧</font>

97
00:06:21,999 --> 00:06:26,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">放心 也就只是失去意识 人还没死</font>

98
00:06:27,269 --> 00:06:31,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然到了机场我就会被捕 但我一个人都没杀</font>

99
00:06:32,969 --> 00:06:36,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在别墅住上一阵子就能出来了</font>

100
00:06:37,889 --> 00:06:40,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦 你真的在骗人</font>

101
00:06:43,049 --> 00:06:44,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">什么意思</font>

102
00:06:45,549 --> 00:06:46,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没什么意思</font>

103
00:06:48,089 --> 00:06:55,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这个侦探啊 我劫持这架飞机确实是有其他原因</font>

104
00:06:55,909 --> 00:07:00,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但我看在你的胆量上 可是故意装输了啊</font>

105
00:07:00,539 --> 00:07:02,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真是的 非要我说出来吗</font>

106
00:07:03,369 --> 00:07:09,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是啊 我们也该学学蝙蝠这种成熟的做法 回到座位上…</font>

107
00:07:09,489 --> 00:07:12,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 我说的「骗人」不是指这个</font>

108
00:07:14,129 --> 00:07:19,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说为了劫机不惜自己的性命 是骗人的吧</font>

109
00:07:20,229 --> 00:07:22,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其实你怕死吧</font>

110
00:07:24,149 --> 00:07:25,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说什么？</font>

111
00:07:27,289 --> 00:07:31,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你认输收手得太快了</font>

112
00:07:32,679 --> 00:07:38,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">敢在这个时代独自劫机的男人 面对一个小女孩</font>

113
00:07:38,139 --> 00:07:40,319
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么可能那么轻易地认输</font>

114
00:07:41,119 --> 00:07:44,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">恐怕你也是受了别人的命令来劫机</font>

115
00:07:45,129 --> 00:07:50,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而那个人命令你和这架飞机一起坠落</font>

116
00:07:50,959 --> 00:07:55,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但其实你很怕死 不想去死</font>

117
00:07:55,339 --> 00:07:58,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为了找到个不死的理由 利用了我们</font>

118
00:08:01,749 --> 00:08:05,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但如果是这样 又为什么做出这种类似推理游戏的举动？</font>

119
00:08:05,849 --> 00:08:12,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不想劫机的话 根本不用这样做 直接老实投降不就好了</font>

120
00:08:12,899 --> 00:08:14,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">他的自尊不允许吧</font>

121
00:08:15,849 --> 00:08:19,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不能不战而败 而是要正经打过一场再认输</font>

122
00:08:19,919 --> 00:08:21,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哪怕只是形式上的</font>

123
00:08:21,769 --> 00:08:23,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是这样的吗</font>

124
00:08:27,259 --> 00:08:28,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂！</font>

125
00:08:29,799 --> 00:08:31,619
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么突然就走人了</font>

126
00:08:33,019 --> 00:08:35,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">事情结束了 我想回座位</font>

127
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:37,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那也别把我丢下啊！</font>

128
00:08:37,819 --> 00:08:40,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我觉得即使不说你自己也会跟上来的</font>

129
00:08:41,879 --> 00:08:42,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂</font>

130
00:08:44,439 --> 00:08:46,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">最后再问你一个问题</font>

131
00:08:48,139 --> 00:08:50,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么你都知道？</font>

132
00:08:53,039 --> 00:08:55,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你凭借什么线索做出这种推理？</font>

133
00:08:55,689 --> 00:09:01,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真的只是因为我认输得太快了？</font>

134
00:09:02,569 --> 00:09:03,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这也是原因之一</font>

135
00:09:04,959 --> 00:09:07,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但我一开始就了解你</font>

136
00:09:09,619 --> 00:09:14,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我了解你今天会上这架飞机 企图劫机</font>

137
00:09:14,329 --> 00:09:18,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">顺便还了解命令你做出这种事的那些同伙</font>

138
00:09:20,939 --> 00:09:27,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为一流的侦探 就要在案子发生前解决案子</font>

139
00:09:30,709 --> 00:09:32,869
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">原来是这样啊</font>

140
00:09:33,719 --> 00:09:38,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哎呀 还好为了以防万一 最后问了你一下</font>

141
00:09:42,129 --> 00:09:43,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手 趴下</font>

142
00:09:46,499 --> 00:09:47,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 你干什么！</font>

143
00:09:51,089 --> 00:09:54,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">抱歉 我改主意了</font>

144
00:09:56,729 --> 00:09:58,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">告诉你一件事</font>

145
00:09:59,289 --> 00:10:01,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一流的特工呢</font>

146
00:10:02,079 --> 00:10:06,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">看到嫩芽 就要在其成长起来之前剪掉</font>

147
00:10:16,899 --> 00:10:17,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂…</font>

148
00:10:18,949 --> 00:10:23,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就不该雇佣什么助手 没想到会这么没用</font>

149
00:10:23,559 --> 00:10:26,789
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不讲道理啊 分明是你强行雇佣我的！</font>

150
00:10:27,129 --> 00:10:29,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不过我也觉得自己没起到什么用处</font>

151
00:10:32,689 --> 00:10:34,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那是什么啊</font>

152
00:10:34,319 --> 00:10:35,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">人造人</font>

153
00:10:37,249 --> 00:10:40,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那个男人是秘密组织「SPES」的成员</font>

154
00:10:40,559 --> 00:10:41,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">SPES？</font>

155
00:10:42,289 --> 00:10:46,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">SPES凭借超越人类知识的力量制造出人造人</font>

156
00:10:46,599 --> 00:10:48,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">暗地里威胁着世界的安全</font>

157
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:51,619
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而那个男人只有耳朵是改造的</font>

158
00:10:52,249 --> 00:10:56,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而且还只是偷了试验品强行安在自己身上</font>

159
00:10:57,409 --> 00:10:59,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也就是半人造人</font>

160
00:11:00,299 --> 00:11:02,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么你连这个都知道</font>

161
00:11:02,449 --> 00:11:08,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而背叛了组织的惩罚 就是他这次接到的命令</font>

162
00:11:08,719 --> 00:11:11,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你倒是说说为什么你连这个都知道啊</font>

163
00:11:12,199 --> 00:11:13,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">难道你也是…</font>

164
00:11:13,849 --> 00:11:16,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗 你连这个都知道</font>

165
00:11:17,429 --> 00:11:18,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">既然如此</font>

166
00:11:19,199 --> 00:11:23,139
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还是把你的尸体带回去当礼物更好啊</font>

167
00:11:24,849 --> 00:11:25,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手</font>

168
00:11:29,929 --> 00:11:32,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">难道你也是人造人？</font>

169
00:11:35,589 --> 00:11:36,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你白痴吗</font>

170
00:11:38,389 --> 00:11:40,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我看起来是怪物？</font>

171
00:11:41,509 --> 00:11:43,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我觉得你这力气和怪物也差不多了</font>

172
00:11:44,839 --> 00:11:47,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">肯定没女生喜欢你吧</font>

173
00:11:49,079 --> 00:11:50,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那是什么啊！</font>

174
00:11:50,819 --> 00:11:53,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大家冷静 请勿奔跑 冷静前往这里避难！</font>

175
00:11:54,489 --> 00:11:58,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哎呀呀 真是满地哀嚎 我最烦这样了</font>

176
00:11:59,339 --> 00:12:01,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">干脆把碍事的人都杀掉吧</font>

177
00:12:01,759 --> 00:12:06,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不要急躁！这样飞机会掉下去 你也会死的！</font>

178
00:12:07,289 --> 00:12:09,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我会留驾驶员一条命的</font>

179
00:12:10,339 --> 00:12:12,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">话说 你到底是谁啊</font>

180
00:12:13,179 --> 00:12:14,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大侦探的助手！</font>

181
00:12:15,919 --> 00:12:16,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦</font>

182
00:12:17,959 --> 00:12:19,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不是 我这就是说漏嘴…</font>

183
00:12:20,639 --> 00:12:24,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">居然叫我大侦探哦 真是个能干的助手</font>

184
00:12:26,819 --> 00:12:27,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手！</font>

185
00:12:33,719 --> 00:12:36,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真是的 这都怎么回事啊</font>

186
00:12:36,319 --> 00:12:38,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你还真的什么都不知道啊</font>

187
00:12:39,289 --> 00:12:43,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">善良的初中生怎么可能知道什么世界的黑幕啊</font>

188
00:12:43,879 --> 00:12:48,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这拿着神秘的提箱去国外的初中生说什么呢？</font>

189
00:12:49,069 --> 00:12:52,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这人到底知道多少事啊？</font>

190
00:12:56,669 --> 00:13:01,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没想到这种地方会有能威胁到我们的人</font>

191
00:13:02,079 --> 00:13:05,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">身为侦探 秘密行事可是基本功</font>

192
00:13:06,179 --> 00:13:09,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你看 你那些同伙就没发现我吧？</font>

193
00:13:10,159 --> 00:13:13,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以我很期待 把你的情报送上去</font>

194
00:13:13,919 --> 00:13:18,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那些没耐心的家伙也许会改主意呢</font>

195
00:13:18,659 --> 00:13:20,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">他们有那么好说话吗？</font>

196
00:13:21,899 --> 00:13:23,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你又懂了？</font>

197
00:13:34,009 --> 00:13:37,319
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 把飞机打出个洞来该怎么办</font>

198
00:13:42,409 --> 00:13:44,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你喘气得挺厉害的嘛</font>

199
00:13:45,599 --> 00:13:47,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个耳朵可是特别订制的</font>

200
00:13:48,149 --> 00:13:50,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">集中在触手末端的听觉细胞</font>

201
00:13:51,169 --> 00:13:55,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">连一百公里外的人类心跳声都能分辨清楚</font>

202
00:13:56,389 --> 00:13:58,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">藏也是没用的</font>

203
00:14:00,059 --> 00:14:04,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">情报还是没搜集齐全 心跳是肯定掩盖不了的</font>

204
00:14:06,139 --> 00:14:07,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如果能有个武器倒还好…</font>

205
00:14:13,579 --> 00:14:14,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔</font>

206
00:14:15,909 --> 00:14:17,269
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">帮我争取30秒</font>

207
00:14:18,229 --> 00:14:19,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我有个想法</font>

208
00:14:21,409 --> 00:14:22,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">明白</font>

209
00:14:41,919 --> 00:14:43,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">让开 让开一下</font>

210
00:14:44,909 --> 00:14:46,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">即使在这种时候…</font>

211
00:14:46,199 --> 00:14:48,329
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 只有在这种时候脑子才特别灵光</font>

212
00:14:49,079 --> 00:14:50,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为天生的招灾体质</font>

213
00:14:51,759 --> 00:14:56,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我遇到的危急场面 比我这辈子吃过的面包还多</font>

214
00:15:12,279 --> 00:15:15,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也该投降了吧 大侦探</font>

215
00:15:25,389 --> 00:15:26,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔！</font>

216
00:15:31,049 --> 00:15:35,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我不知道那个箱子里有什么 但是…</font>

217
00:15:36,129 --> 00:15:40,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个直觉 肯定是我综合过去的经验得出的最优解！</font>

218
00:15:42,069 --> 00:15:42,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">接住！</font>

219
00:15:43,009 --> 00:15:44,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">休想！</font>

220
00:15:52,069 --> 00:15:52,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手</font>

221
00:15:56,529 --> 00:15:58,139
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">干得漂亮</font>

222
00:16:00,629 --> 00:16:04,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">案子还没结束呢 大侦探！</font>

223
00:16:07,189 --> 00:16:08,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是啊 然而…</font>

224
00:16:09,159 --> 00:16:12,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">既然有我在场 就和已经解决了没什么两样</font>

225
00:16:38,349 --> 00:16:38,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">砰！</font>

226
00:16:40,609 --> 00:16:43,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好 现在你已经死了</font>

227
00:16:47,029 --> 00:16:53,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这样你就不会被你的同伙追杀 因为你已经是个死人了</font>

228
00:16:55,049 --> 00:16:56,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你在耍我吗？</font>

229
00:16:57,129 --> 00:16:59,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你不是不想死吗？</font>

230
00:17:00,519 --> 00:17:06,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我会让日本警察压下这件事 对外就说你已经死了</font>

231
00:17:06,989 --> 00:17:09,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没事 我有信得过的人脉</font>

232
00:17:11,359 --> 00:17:14,789
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不在这里杀了我 你会后悔的</font>

233
00:17:15,219 --> 00:17:15,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么？</font>

234
00:17:19,899 --> 00:17:20,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔！</font>

235
00:17:27,109 --> 00:17:31,329
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">刚才打中你的子弹 是用我的血制造的</font>

236
00:17:32,329 --> 00:17:36,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">沐浴过血的人 会变得绝对无法违逆主人</font>

237
00:17:37,329 --> 00:17:42,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也就是说 你的触手再也不能攻击我了</font>

238
00:17:44,499 --> 00:17:46,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这什么原理啊</font>

239
00:17:47,439 --> 00:17:48,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是商业机密</font>

240
00:17:50,089 --> 00:17:52,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你也是被谁指使来的吗？</font>

241
00:17:52,679 --> 00:17:53,319
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不</font>

242
00:17:54,559 --> 00:17:57,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是与生俱来的大侦探体质</font>

243
00:18:15,139 --> 00:18:16,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">说起来 谢丝塔啊</font>

244
00:18:18,459 --> 00:18:21,749
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说你在子弹上做了特殊的手脚…</font>

245
00:18:22,489 --> 00:18:25,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是什么时候动手的啊？</font>

246
00:18:27,259 --> 00:18:28,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你是白痴吗</font>

247
00:18:30,239 --> 00:18:32,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么可能有那种时间</font>

248
00:18:32,779 --> 00:18:35,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那是我一开始就准备好的</font>

249
00:18:35,879 --> 00:18:37,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一开始就…</font>

250
00:18:37,969 --> 00:18:38,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">难道？</font>

251
00:18:39,219 --> 00:18:43,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没错 下令让你带着那个提箱上飞机的人</font>

252
00:18:44,619 --> 00:18:45,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就是我</font>

253
00:18:48,239 --> 00:18:52,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也就是说 我一开始就被你玩弄在股掌之间？</font>

254
00:18:52,599 --> 00:18:56,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你要怪也只能怪没能摆脱我的自己了</font>

255
00:18:58,689 --> 00:19:00,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不讲道理啊</font>

256
00:19:01,779 --> 00:19:04,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">说起来 你为什么找我…</font>

257
00:19:05,639 --> 00:19:06,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">人呢？</font>

258
00:19:08,999 --> 00:19:09,319
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(国际机场)</font>

259
00:19:09,319 --> 00:19:10,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔？
(国际机场)</font>

260
00:19:10,379 --> 00:19:12,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(国际机场)</font>

261
00:19:20,089 --> 00:19:21,599
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">累死了</font>

262
00:19:23,859 --> 00:19:26,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那到底是怎么回事啊</font>

263
00:19:35,359 --> 00:19:38,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不不 不能再被牵扯进去了</font>

264
00:19:39,269 --> 00:19:39,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">欢迎回来</font>

265
00:19:46,639 --> 00:19:48,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你真慢啊</font>

266
00:19:55,249 --> 00:19:59,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(第1集 请问乘客之中有没有侦探？)</font>

267
00:19:59,999 --> 00:20:01,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我说过很多次了…</font>

268
00:20:03,569 --> 00:20:04,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我拒绝！</font>

269
00:20:04,849 --> 00:20:06,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">咦？你说啥？</font>

270
00:20:06,689 --> 00:20:08,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不要假装没听到！</font>

271
00:20:08,999 --> 00:20:12,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我说的是我不想当你的助手</font>

272
00:20:14,729 --> 00:20:15,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">听不清</font>

273
00:20:16,229 --> 00:20:16,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂！</font>

274
00:20:17,699 --> 00:20:20,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好啦 你冷静点</font>

275
00:20:20,919 --> 00:20:22,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要不我帮你搓搓背？</font>

276
00:20:24,189 --> 00:20:25,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">免了</font>

277
00:20:25,949 --> 00:20:28,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要不我只裹着浴巾进去？</font>

278
00:20:31,169 --> 00:20:32,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">免了</font>

279
00:20:33,259 --> 00:20:35,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真是清晰可见的迟疑</font>

280
00:20:36,339 --> 00:20:40,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">可恶 这女人居然对青春期的男生用这么卑鄙的招数</font>

281
00:20:41,279 --> 00:20:47,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而且 重点在于 这一周里我都跟你说了多少遍了！</font>

282
00:20:47,609 --> 00:20:52,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不许擅闯别人家！不要擅闯浴室！</font>

283
00:20:52,629 --> 00:20:56,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还不是都怪你不肯接受我的提议？</font>

284
00:20:56,199 --> 00:20:58,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这种事情谁能接受啊</font>

285
00:20:58,669 --> 00:21:03,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只是要你当我的助手 全世界到处飞而已嘛</font>

286
00:21:04,309 --> 00:21:07,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这种莫名其妙的要求 换谁都会拒绝的</font>

287
00:21:09,349 --> 00:21:15,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你可真够固执的 要闯入你家可也不是件轻松活儿哦</font>

288
00:21:15,859 --> 00:21:19,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你怎么还这么得意呢？还是我的错了？</font>

289
00:21:19,299 --> 00:21:22,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">话说我不是上了锁吗？</font>

290
00:21:22,399 --> 00:21:25,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦 我用万能钥匙打开的</font>

291
00:21:26,499 --> 00:21:31,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是我的「七道具」之一哦 没有它打不开的锁</font>

292
00:21:31,909 --> 00:21:34,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这非法入侵不是挺轻松的嘛</font>

293
00:21:35,969 --> 00:21:37,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这说得就有点过分了</font>

294
00:21:37,819 --> 00:21:40,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">总没有侵犯隐私权的某人过分</font>

295
00:21:41,829 --> 00:21:46,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那么 你为何会如此不愿意当我的助手呢？</font>

296
00:21:50,009 --> 00:21:54,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我之前不是说过了 因为我这招灾体质</font>

297
00:21:54,069 --> 00:21:56,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">从小到大就没遇到过什么好事</font>

298
00:21:57,019 --> 00:22:03,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以我的梦想 就是在和平中度过不温不火的生活</font>

299
00:22:03,929 --> 00:22:06,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">意思是和我在一起就过不了这种生活？</font>

300
00:22:07,989 --> 00:22:09,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还用说吗</font>

301
00:22:13,689 --> 00:22:17,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">和那种东西扯上关系 几条命都不够用的</font>

302
00:22:17,979 --> 00:22:21,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是 这份工作 只有我能做</font>

303
00:22:23,719 --> 00:22:27,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那把我牵扯进只有你能做的这工作里 有什么意义？</font>

304
00:22:28,689 --> 00:22:29,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个…</font>

305
00:22:31,019 --> 00:22:32,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">啊 对了</font>

306
00:22:32,119 --> 00:22:34,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这是想临时凑个借口来糊弄我吧？</font>

307
00:22:34,919 --> 00:22:36,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其实我对你一见钟情啦</font>

308
00:22:37,109 --> 00:22:42,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不不 第一次见面的时候你明显对我的脸没什么感觉吧</font>

309
00:22:42,659 --> 00:22:48,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这脸只要两天没见就会被人遗忘 很适合做地下工作哦</font>

310
00:22:48,849 --> 00:22:54,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不要明褒暗贬了 也不要马上给我分配助手的工作</font>

311
00:22:56,579 --> 00:22:59,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你真的不给我当助手？</font>

312
00:23:00,139 --> 00:23:02,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么还有点消沉了</font>

313
00:23:05,539 --> 00:23:09,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">话说 既然要谈判 不该先说说好处吗？</font>

314
00:23:12,159 --> 00:23:14,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没想到你人还挺好的嘛</font>

315
00:23:14,749 --> 00:23:16,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">过奖了</font>

316
00:23:16,779 --> 00:23:20,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">说起来 刚才我点了披萨外卖 行吗？</font>

317
00:23:20,399 --> 00:23:24,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不要马上就利用别人的善良啊！而且这是本周第5次了！</font>

318
00:23:24,389 --> 00:23:26,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">马上给我打电话去取消！</font>

319
00:23:26,839 --> 00:23:31,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">以我的预想来看呢 也许直到1年之后</font>

320
00:23:31,119 --> 00:23:34,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我们也会像现在这样开开心心的</font>

321
00:23:34,399 --> 00:23:38,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一点都不开心好吗！就只是我一直在闹心！</font>

322
00:23:41,029 --> 00:23:42,159
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以</font>

323
00:23:43,169 --> 00:23:44,289
