539
00:37:19,209 --> 00:37:21,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">他们都以为这是角色扮演活动吧</font>

540
00:37:22,529 --> 00:37:23,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂</font>

541
00:37:24,539 --> 00:37:25,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真开心啊 助手</font>

542
00:37:29,179 --> 00:37:30,749
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 谁是助手啊！</font>

543
00:37:31,319 --> 00:37:32,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦 发现了？</font>

544
00:37:34,559 --> 00:37:35,649
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手 那里</font>

545
00:37:39,199 --> 00:37:40,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">想逃到校外去吗</font>

546
00:37:43,709 --> 00:37:46,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">等等 我有不好的预感</font>

547
00:37:47,119 --> 00:37:50,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你该不会是想从这里跳下去吧</font>

548
00:37:51,449 --> 00:37:52,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 你说错了</font>

549
00:37:53,129 --> 00:37:55,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗 我就说不至于嘛</font>

550
00:37:55,929 --> 00:37:58,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不是我一个人 你也要一起跳</font>

551
00:38:00,529 --> 00:38:06,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没事 我现在穿的鞋子 是大侦探的七道具之一</font>

552
00:38:08,769 --> 00:38:10,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">能在天上飞哦</font>

553
00:38:30,389 --> 00:38:34,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这就是不来上学的学生们服用的药物</font>

554
00:38:35,139 --> 00:38:39,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">服下之后会暂时变得情绪昂扬 注意力更加集中</font>

555
00:38:40,539 --> 00:38:43,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以以田径社的学生为中心慢慢扩散开来了</font>

556
00:38:44,339 --> 00:38:46,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我都没听说过…</font>

557
00:38:47,159 --> 00:38:51,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是 也有因副作用而导致记忆障碍的案例</font>

558
00:38:52,159 --> 00:38:56,849
