<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在回想起来…</font>

576
00:40:14,999 --> 00:40:18,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔是一开始就装成客人</font>

577
00:40:19,369 --> 00:40:22,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">用暗语偷偷和花子小姐取得了联系</font>

578
00:40:25,229 --> 00:40:26,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我不是说了吗</font>

579
00:40:26,569 --> 00:40:32,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一流的侦探 就要在案子发生前解决案子</font>

580
00:40:33,219 --> 00:40:37,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好吧 对你来说这也算不上什么疑难案件</font>

581
00:40:38,479 --> 00:40:39,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是</font>

582
00:40:40,759 --> 00:40:45,639
