<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是我唯一的答案</font>

603
00:42:25,959 --> 00:42:27,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我会保护你</font>

604
00:42:29,069 --> 00:42:33,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不管你被你的体质拖累 牵扯到多大的案子和麻烦之中</font>

605
00:42:33,469 --> 00:42:36,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我都会奋不顾身地保护你</font>

606
00:42:37,309 --> 00:42:37,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以</font>

607
00:42:39,619 --> 00:42:42,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你来当我的助手吧</font>

608
00:42:47,459 --> 00:42:50,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你以为说这种漂亮话就能忽悠我吗？</font>

609
00:42:51,309 --> 00:42:54,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这种假大空的提议…</font>

